Third-party components and per-file attributions are listed in CREDITS.md.

Notable derivations:

  - The +D, DISCiPLE, Didaktik, Multiface and Interface 1 peripheral
    implementations are JavaScript ports of Fuse 1.8.0 (GPL v2+) C
    source. Each ported file carries an "Ported from Fuse 1.8.0 ..."
    header. Fuse is Copyright (C) Philip Kendall, Stuart Brady,
    Fredrick Meunier, Gergely Szasz, Dmitry Sanarin, Darren Salt and
    many others.

  - The Z80 core, framebuffer renderer, audio engine, base UI shell
    and the Beta128 / UPD765 FDCs are from JSSpeccy 3 by Matt Westcott.

System ROMs shipped under static/roms/ are subject to Amstrad plc's
emulation-use permission; they are not covered by GPL v3.
